text: Diaz (Romualdez) is one of 9 Barangays of the municipality of Tubajon, Dinagat Islands, Philippines. ==Education== The barangay hosts the Mauro Diaz Elementary School which was established, January 01, 1975 and is part of the Tubajon District.Mauro Diaz Elementary School == References == == External links == * Province of Dinagat Islands - Official webpage * Mauro Diaz Elementary School - Diaz (Romualdez), Dinagat Islands Category:Philippines geography stubs Category:Barangays of Dinagat Islands
